label: Membership or Pass Type
description: The membership or pass type of the MetroBike user. More info at : https://austin.bcycle.com/passes

label: Bicycle ID
description: The MetroBike's ID that was rented during the trip

label: Bike Type
description: The type of bicycle used for the trip

label: Checkout Datetime
description: The date and time that the bike was checked out from the MetroBike kiosk.

label: Checkout Date
description: The date the bike was checked out from the kiosk.

label: Checkout Time
description: The time the bike was checked out for the trip.

label: Checkout Kiosk ID
description: The Kiosk ID of the Kiosk that was used to checkout the bicycle.

label: Checkout Kiosk
description: The location of the checkout Kiosk based on its nearby cross streets.

label: Return Kiosk ID
description: The ID of the Kiosk that was used to return the bicycle.

label: Return Kiosk
description: The location of the Kiosk to return the bicycle. Based on the location's the nearby cross-streets.

label: Trip Duration Minutes
description: The total number of minutes that the bicycle was checked out.

label: Month
description: The calendar month on which the trip began

label: Year
description: The year in which the trip began
